text: Stela is a Romanian feminine given name. Notable persons with that name include: *Stela Perin (born 1934), Romanian artistic gymnast *Stela Popa (born 1982), Moldovan journalist and author *Stela Popescu (born 1935), Romanian actress *Stela Pura (born 1971), Romanian swimmer *Stela Namar (born 1978), Swiss fashion designer Category:Romanian feminine given names
